<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Modern Sticky Navigation</title>
    
    <!-- Importing a modern Google Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        
        :root {
            --green-deep: #064e3b;
            --green-1: #059669;
            --green-2: #10b981;
            --green-3: #34d399;
            --green-light: #ecfdf5;
            --text-main: #1f2937;
            --text-light: #ffffff;
            --bg-color: #f6fef9;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            --transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth; 
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-main);
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px; 
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 95%;
            max-width: 1100px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 50px; /* Pill shape */
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        header.scrolled {
            top: 10px;
            width: 98%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.15); 
            border-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.3);
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-1), var(--green-3));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        header.scrolled .logo {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.3);
        }

        .nav-menu {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 10px;
            position: relative; 
        }

        .nav-item {
            position: relative;
        }

        
        .nav-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-1), var(--green-3));
            border-radius: 30px;
            z-index: 0;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.4);
            pointer-events: none; 
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .nav-link {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 22px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1; 
        }

        .nav-link:hover, .nav-link.active {
            color: var(--text-light);
            text-shadow: none;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .hamburger {
            display: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .bar {
            display: block;
            width: 25px;
            height: 3px;
            margin: 5px auto;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-1), var(--green-3));
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }

        section {
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 120px 20px 60px; 
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            padding: 60px 40px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.05);
            transition: var(--transition);
            max-width: 1000px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        section:hover .content-wrapper {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.15);
            border-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.4);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-deep), var(--green-2));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        section:hover .section-title {
            text-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.3);
        }

        .section-desc {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #4b5563;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        
        .services-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 30px 24px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            text-align: left;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.4);
        }

        .service-icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-light), #ffffff);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--green-1);
            font-size: 24px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.2);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .service-card:hover .service-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-1), var(--green-2));
            color: white;
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--green-deep);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .service-card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        
        .portfolio-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .portfolio-card {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: var(--transition);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            background-color: #eaeaea;
        }

        .portfolio-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .portfolio-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.95), rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.3));
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: left;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(15px);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .portfolio-card:hover .portfolio-overlay {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .portfolio-card:hover .portfolio-img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .portfolio-overlay h4 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .portfolio-overlay p {
            color: var(--green-3);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Contact Section Details & Forms */
        .contact-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
            gap: 40px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 35px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .contact-info {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            transition: var(--transition);
            color: #ecfdf5;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .info-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            transform: translateX(6px);
            border-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.3);
        }

        .info-icon {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.2);
            color: var(--green-3);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .info-text h5 {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: var(--green-3);
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .info-text p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .contact-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .form-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            color: #a7f3d0;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-left: 4px;
        }

        .form-control {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            color: white;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--green-2);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.25);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
        }

        .submit-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-1), var(--green-2));
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.3);
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .submit-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.5);
        }

        #home {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-light) 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        }
        
        #home::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 20%; left: 15%;
            width: 400px; height: 400px;
            background: var(--green-3);
            filter: blur(120px);
            opacity: 0.15;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        #about { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, var(--green-light) 100%); }
        #services { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-light) 0%, #ffffff 100%); }
        #portfolio { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, var(--green-light) 100%); }
        
        #contact {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-deep) 0%, var(--green-1) 100%);
        }
        #contact .content-wrapper {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        #contact:hover .content-wrapper {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.5);
        }
        #contact .section-title {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a7f3d0, #ffffff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
        }
        #contact .section-desc { color: #a7f3d0; }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-40px) scale(1.05); }
        }

        
        .hero-tag {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--green-1);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            background: var(--green-light);
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.2);
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .cta-btn {
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .cta-btn.primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-1), var(--green-2));
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.3);
        }

        .cta-btn.primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.5);
        }

        .cta-btn.secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            color: var(--green-deep);
            border: 1px solid rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }

        .cta-btn.secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1);
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .stat-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--green-deep);
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .stat-divider {
            width: 1px;
            height: 40px;
            background: rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.15);
        }

        /* About Section Grid */
        .mb-40 {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .about-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 35px 24px;
            text-align: left;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .about-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.3);
        }

        .about-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-light), #ffffff);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--green-1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.2);
        }

        .about-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--green-deep);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .about-card p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #4b5563;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                width: 90%;
                padding: 12px 20px;
            }
            
            .nav-indicator {
                display: none !important;
            }

            .nav-link:hover {
                color: var(--green-1);
                background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.1);
                text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.5);
            }

            .nav-link.active {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green-1), var(--green-3));
                color: var(--text-light);
                box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.4);
                text-shadow: none;
            }
            
            header.scrolled {
                width: 95%;
            }

            .hamburger {
                display: block;
                padding: 5px 10px; 
                margin-right: -10px;
            }

            .nav-menu {
                position: absolute;
                top: 100%; 
                left: 0;
                margin-top: 15px; 
                transform: translateY(-15px); 
                flex-direction: column;
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98); 
                backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
                -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
                width: 100%;
                border-radius: 25px;
                padding: 20px;
                box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.2);
                border: 1px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.3);
                opacity: 0;
                visibility: hidden;
                transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
                gap: 5px;
            }

            .nav-menu.active {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
                visibility: visible;
            }

            .nav-link {
                display: block;
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 12px;
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .hamburger.active .bar:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
            .hamburger.active .bar:nth-child(1) {
                transform: translateY(8px) rotate(45deg);
                background: var(--green-deep);
            }
            .hamburger.active .bar:nth-child(3) {
                transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(-45deg);
                background: var(--green-deep);
            }

            .section-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .content-wrapper { padding: 40px 20px; }

            .contact-layout {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 30px;
            }

            .stat-divider {
                display: none;
            }
            .hero-stats {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header & Navigation -->
    <header id="header">
        <nav>
            <a href="#home" class="logo">NexGen.</a>
            
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <!-- Added sliding indicator element -->
                <li class="nav-indicator" aria-hidden="true"></li>
                
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#home" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#about" class="nav-link">About</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#services" class="nav-link">Services</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#portfolio" class="nav-link">Portfolio</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a href="#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Mobile Hamburger Icon -->
            <div class="hamburger">
                <span class="bar"></span>
                <span class="bar"></span>
                <span class="bar"></span>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Sample Page Sections with Glassmorphism Wrappers -->
    <main>
        <section id="home">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="hero-tag">NEXGEN DIGITAL ECOSYSTEMS</div>
                <h1 class="section-title">Architecting Sustainable Web Experiences</h1>
                <p class="section-desc">We build lightning-fast digital solutions using environmentally friendly coding patterns and premium glassmorphism layouts that automatically adapt across every device.</p>
                
                <div class="hero-actions">
                    <a href="#services" class="cta-btn primary">Explore Services</a>
                    <a href="#about" class="cta-btn secondary">Who We Are</a>
                </div>

                <div class="hero-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">99.9%</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Eco-Friendly Uptime</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-divider"></div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">150+</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Projects Completed</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-divider"></div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <span class="stat-number">25ms</span>
                        <span class="stat-label">Avg Interaction Latency</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <h2 class="section-title">About Our Mission</h2>
                <p class="section-desc mb-40">We combine premium glassmorphism effects with vibrant green neon accents to build deeply immersive and highly scalable web architectures.</p>
                
                <div class="about-grid">
                    <div class="about-card">
                        <div class="about-icon">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20.24 12.24a6 6 0 0 0-8.49-8.49L5 10.5V19h8.5z"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4>Our Mission</h4>
                        <p>To design lightweight, blazing-fast interfaces that drastically reduce internet-related power grids while retaining absolute visual prestige and user flow.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="about-card">
                        <div class="about-icon">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16V12M12 8h.01"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h4>Our Philosophy</h4>
                        <p>We treat web environments as living systems. Combining kinetic feedback layers, glass reflections, and responsive modules allows users to connect naturally.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Dynamic Services Section -->
        <section id="services">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <h2 class="section-title">Our Services</h2>
                <p class="section-desc">We provide modular and scalable digital engineering with modern architecture standards.</p>
                
                <div class="services-grid">
                    <!-- Service 1 -->
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <div class="service-icon">
                            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Interactive Web Apps</h3>
                        <p>We build highly performant, responsive web apps using cutting-edge design guidelines and optimized states.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Service 2 -->
